者San Francisco，廣東話就講返三藩市，真係好少聽人係三藩市講San Fran依兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcdfaff0a17ae871d54a16fcf095ea9eef19bc6","tid":340612,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"讀生藩"},{"pid":"44fb4b752cf03ce8396cdf877e8bebc7aa78be71","tid":340612,"uid":69320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T20:58:37.000Z","msg":"叫開 「腥 fo」&larr;唔識打個音 類似prot-fo-lio個fo但第2聲<br />\n咁叫係因為個airport code係SFO <br />\n<br />\nby airline staff"},{"pid":"92f62f3184901e4a586b85a6904908093eeaea8d","tid":340612,"uid":27509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫開 「腥 fo」&larr;唔識打個音 類似prot-fo-lio個fo但第2聲<br />\n咁叫係因為個airport code係SFO <br />\n<br />\nby airline staff</blockquote><br />\n你個讀音仲難聽過san fran<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會讀s-f-o番工果陣<br />\nby travel agent"},{"pid":"bc61f8c9b24f2b10899c3ea8429913ecc3e57bfc","tid":340612,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫開 「腥 fo」&larr;唔識打個音 類似prot-fo-lio個fo但第2聲<br />\n咁叫係因為個airport code係SFO <br />\n<br />\nby airline staff</blockquote><br />\n你不如直接讀osas算啦"},{"pid":"a0bb9ba892f876d5d6d37897d89f67eb60a17896","tid":340612,"uid":71584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:29:12.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都有咁叫 or city"},{"pid":"7916e29a623b99487a75c6481001b6065a3b0789","tid":340612,"uid":126681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:38:10.000Z","msg":"反正都係個名。大把人咁叫 <br />\n<br />\n利申 住係到"},{"pid":"4110c639e4233259f4d8751b2b58dfc5a20f4c1c","tid":340612,"uid":69320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫開 「腥 fo」&larr;唔識打個音 類似prot-fo-lio個fo但第2聲<br />\n咁叫係因為個airport code係SFO <br />\n<br />\nby airline staff</blockquote><br />\n你個讀音